 class="type" style="color:#EAB766">string</span> on success.  </p> </div>  <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.dgettext-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <span>   <ul class="simplelist">    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link gettext()} - Lookup a message in the current domain</span></li>   </ul>  </span> </div></div>
